# Registers the ccd-case-document-am-client autoconfiguration in the Spring Boot 4 format
# (replacing spring.factories which is no longer supported in Spring Boot 4). Required so
# the class can be excluded via spring.autoconfigure.exclude in application.yaml until
# the library is updated for Spring Boot 4 compatibility.
uk.gov.hmcts.reform.ccd.document.am.config.CaseDocumentManagementClientAutoConfiguration
